修复在pg_clog和pg_subtrans文件创建期间会导致<quote>文件早已存在</>
错误的竞态条件 (Tom)
</para>
</listitem>

<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Fix cases that could lead to crashes if a cache-invalidation
message arrives at just the wrong time (Tom)</para>
